{"tid":741114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同大陸親戚去酒樓食飯，佢地話要開電視睇新聞","createTime":"2018-07-13T11:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T15:56:31.000Z","uid":29625,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0dff59aa75a45d2ae768e8616763b6c2184014d4","tid":741114,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"跟住就較咗去33台睇CCTV新聞聯播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母痴撚線<br />\n頭十分鐘喺度捧習總、講支共黨務<br />\n有五分鐘用嚟踩港獨台獨民進黨<br />\n<br />\n中間十分鐘報天災，白事當紅事報<br />\n<br />\n最後十分鐘打飛機講支那點點點威水<br />\n貿易戰踩鳩美國<br />\n<br />\n問佢地覺得咁嘅新聞有咩好睇<br />\n唔覺得好偏頗㗎咩？<br />\n佢地話睇慣咗吖嘛<br />\n跟住成半粒鐘都喺度對住部電視講中國點好習總點辛苦<br />\n<br />\n佢地當中仲有人已經拎咗香港身份證好多年<br />\n喺香港落地生根成埋家<br />\n<br />\n一諗起有幾多香港出世蝗蟲仔係由細睇呢啲<br />\n節目睇到大就無晒胃口<br />\n成餐都背脊骨落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bda242e3ac13498000c1fd953109701dea64a4","tid":741114,"uid":9564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:47:22.000Z","msg":"洒樓會特登轉去33？，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dac8a159a323be56a698d421fc435fb02b447d4","tid":741114,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47bda242e3ac13498000c1fd953109701dea64a4","tid":741114,"uid":9564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:47:22.000Z","msg":"洒樓會特登轉去33？，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"房有獨立電視有遙控"},{"pid":"dcc07180173fe1350c1d9f4acbae71de2c4f510e","tid":741114,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"唔出奇<br />\n而家電視台訪問啲新移民<br />\n都影住佢地部電視係長開33"},{"pid":"948975a889bba8d45f6fc781615c5304ad6ddc3e","tid":741114,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcc07180173fe1350c1d9f4acbae71de2c4f510e","tid":741114,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20